        en:"At the eastern end of piazzale Malatesti, the itinerary follows the route of the ancient parapet walk along the Malatesta walls. The wall at this point runs parallel to the Adriatic coast as far as the site of the ex Porta Marina (today piazzale Rosselli) where, from the bastion, it was once possible to look out over the coastal orchards and fields to the sea."
